content.rendered:
Directed by Venu Sriram.

Written by Ramana Dumpala. Venu Sriram. Mamidala Thirupathi. Srikanth Vissa.

Cast Nani(Nani). Sai Pallavi(Pallavi). Bhoomika Chawla(Jyothi). Rajeev Kanakala(Nani’s brother (as Rajiv Kanakala)). Vijay Varma(Warangal Siva). V.K. Naresh(Nani’s uncle). Aamani(Nani’s aunt). Priyadarshi Pulikonda(Darshan (Darshi) (as Priyadarshi)). Krishna Murali Posani(Pallavi’s father). Pavitra Lokesh(Shiva Shakthi’s Mother (as Pavithra Lokesh)). Vennela Kishore(Kishore). Mahadevan(RTO Officer). Racha Ravi(Nani’s friend). Ashrita Vemuganti(Doctor). Subhalekha Sudhakar(D. Srinivas) .Arpitha.Dhanvi.R.J. Hemant.Jyothi.Kiran.Ravi Kiran.Krishnateja.Roopa Lakshmi.Isha Lavanya.Mani.Pranavi.Pravalika.Rama Raju.Rakesh.Ramani.Ramu.Ramesh Reddy.Surender Reddy.Ritesh.Sagar.Sainath.Shyam.Siri.Sravan.Sridevi.Srinivas.Subhash.Sudharshan.Sudigali Sudheer.Swetha.Rakesh Varre.Gagan Vihari.Vijay

Language Telugu.

Producers Ivano Fucci. Lakshman. Dil Raju. Harshith Reddy. Sireesh.

Production Dil Raju Productio. Goldmines Telefilm. Sri Venkateswara Creation.
